rComments: Honestly one of the best instructors I've had as of yet. Makes an effort to step through lectures slowly and deliberately. Almost everything was crystal clear, especially if you read a bit about the topic in the textbook beforehand.
the best professor i have had in this university so far.

I'm currently taking this class since it is a year course, and I really like his teaching style. He actually takes his time and makes sure the class understands something before moving on. It is an average paced class. Not too slow and not too fast. Makes calculus more bearable.
very patient and maybe suitable for students who prefer a slow pace. examples given in class can help better understanding
